results.description:
Etch is an intelligent personal CRM / Contact Management app that helps you remember all the people you meet. 

Using artificial intelligence, Etch automatically helps you identify and memorize every bit of information associated with each of your contacts, including professional biographies, communication histories, and even social media updates. With all these data, Etch transforms your personal network into a powerful database, where so you can easily find the right people that you need.

Etch helps you automate 4 of the most painful steps in networking:
 -  Automatically merge contacts from multiple sources, and get rid of duplicate ones
 -  Intelligently research each contact, and enrich their profile information with professional biographies and social media updates
 -  Aggregate historical interactions from multiple sources, such as emails, calls, and meetings in a unified timeline
 -  Allow you to search for people from all the data mentioned above

Etch is the 1 stop solution to mastering your relationship game. Find out more at https://etch.ai/ 

Reach out to help@etch.ai if you have any questions or requests.
